{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Jbh9oD7gwB5R4JpHCSBAvq","type":"tool_result","content":"*   Trying ::1:34443...\n* Connected to localhost (::1) port 34443 (#0)\n> GET /orders HTTP/1.1\r\n> Host: localhost:34443\r\n> User-Agent: curl/7.76.1\r\n> Accept: */*\r\n> \r\n* Mark bundle as not supporting multiuse\n< HTTP/1.1 200 OK\r\n< Content-Type: text/html;charset=UTF-8\r\n< Content-Language: en-US\r\n< Content-Length: 3032\r\n< Date: Tue, 17 Mar 2026 03:42:32 GMT\r\n< \r\n{ [3032 bytes data]\n* Connection #0 to host localhost left intact\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <title>Order Java Persistence Example</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/default.css\"/>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1>Order Java Persistence Example</h1>\n\n    <h2>View All Orders</h2>\n    <table rules=\"all\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n        <tr>\n            <th>Order ID</th>\n            <th>Shipment Info</th>","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e80e1467-8d50-4d14-a21d-b94c86ec6299","uuid":"9268a582-d0c0-4d32-a11d-ef9cc60e8687"}
