{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01E4HBzx9BLUfzLjHGhQWKMr","type":"tool_result","content":"*   Trying ::1:34443...\n* Connected to localhost (::1) port 34443 (#0)\n> GET /css/default.css HTTP/1.1\r\n> Host: localhost:34443\r\n> User-Agent: curl/7.76.1\r\n> Accept: */*\r\n> \r\n* Mark bundle as not supporting multiuse\n< HTTP/1.1 404 Not Found\r\n< Content-Language: en-US\r\n< Content-Length: 0\r\n< Connection: Close\r\n< Date: Tue, 17 Mar 2026 03:42:56 GMT\r\n< \r\n* Closing connection 0","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e80e1467-8d50-4d14-a21d-b94c86ec6299","uuid":"8ea3944e-cf6d-47df-9c10-9f09fcd0ff62"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01J2ThC8qLEHPjeia44sevCy","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The CSS returns 404. This is because JAX-RS with `@ApplicationPath(\"/\")` is intercepting all requests. I need to change the application path to something more specific, or add a static resource handler. The simplest fix is to change `@ApplicationPath(\"/\")` to `@ApplicationPath(\"/api\")` but then all our endpoints would be at `/api/orders`, etc., which would break the form actions.\n\nThe better approach is to keep the JAX-RS at `/` but add a CSS-serving endpoint, or better yet, move static files to be served by the servlet container. With Liberty, the order of resolution is: exact servlet mapping > JAX-RS. Since our JAX-RS only maps specific paths, the CSS should actually work if it's not caught.\n\nWait - the issue is that JAX-RS doesn't have a mapping for `/css/*`, so it returns 404. The servlet container should serve it. But it's not. Let me check if the CSS file is actually in the WAR:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":383,"cache_read_input_tokens":133359,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":383,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":373},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e80e1467-8d50-4d14-a21d-b94c86ec6299","uuid":"62f2c2eb-a9f0-4fe4-9a7d-30b191c437ab"}
