{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_012ZBAUtvAcPthV54y2aa4pv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now, I also suspect the issue might be in the `lineItems.html` template. Let me look at the `<title>` tag:\n\n```html\n<title>Line Items for Order <span th:text=\"${currentOrder}\"></span></title>\n```\n\nThe `<span>` tag inside `<title>` is not valid in HTML parsing mode and could cause issues. But the error is on orders.html. Let me look at orders.html more carefully. The `@{/lineItems(orderId=${order.orderId})}` syntax - this is Thymeleaf Standard URL syntax. Let me check if there's a syntax issue.\n\nActually, looking at the template again, the `@{...}` syntax with parameters uses Thymeleaf's link expression. The issue could be that the template parser encounters an `@{...}` expression which is a \"link\" expression, and the Standard dialect properly supports it. This should be fine.\n\nWait - the issue might be the `th:if=\"${findVendorTableDisabled}\"`. If this is null, Thymeleaf should handle it. Let me think about what else could go wrong...\n\nActually, the \"template parsing\" error is different from a \"template execution\" error. A parsing error means the template syntax itself is invalid. Let me look more carefully at the HTML...\n\nI see it now - in `orders.html` line 22:\n```html\n<a th:href=\"@{/lineItems(orderId=${order.orderId})}\" th:text=\"${order.orderId}\"></a>\n```\n\nThis uses Thymeleaf's standard link expression syntax. This should be valid. Let me check if there might be special characters causing parsing issues. Let me also check if the template files have any encoding issues:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":788,"cache_read_input_tokens":42682,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":788,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":524},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e80e1467-8d50-4d14-a21d-b94c86ec6299","uuid":"05f8fdc5-bd8a-4624-bfd0-392ac74f76e8"}
